Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: It's not every day\Nthe Princesses pass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,all their responsibilities\Non to you and your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna: You wanted to boost\NTwilight's confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so you brought back Chrysalis,\NCozy Glow, and Tirek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to attack her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord was Grogar!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.65,0:00:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been setting up\Nchallenges for us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole time,\Nhaven't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} The ultimate battle for the{\i0}\N{\i1} fate of Equestria ...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} is coming!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack: We'll hold them\Ntill you get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord: Fly, you foal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy Glow: And NOW for your\Ncomplete DESTRUCTION!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't that be FUN?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis:\NPatience, Cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Destruction\Nis so... permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to show the\Nrest of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've broken\Ntheir heroes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.42,0:01:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we should have\Nfun with our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No! We should hunt\Ndown Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as she's out\Nthere, she's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that big\N{\i1}strong{\i0} minotaur
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT scared of\None little pony? Relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like her friends\Nare going anywhere..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The fools brought the remains\Nof my throne to Canterlot
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those shards block\Ntheir magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful. Too close and the\Nshards cancel even our powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:01:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But on THIS side\Nof the cavern,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we're the most powerful\Nbeings in Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks to Grogar's Bell.\NIsn't that right... GROGAR?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,when you tried to take\NDiscord's chaos magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but there's\Nalicorn princess magic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in there now too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be sooo much more\Npowerful if I just could have..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean\NYOU could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um hello, I'm the best one out\Nof all of us, nobody sees me--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are you talking about!?\N-The best at what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta find Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably already\Nfigured out some way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to defeat those monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Any idea HOW we get\Nout of here to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Too sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way anypony\Ncould get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord: I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It made so much\Nsense in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight defeats\Nher worst enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and is filled\Nwith confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly did have\Nthe best intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll make\Nit up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT'S gonna need to be\Na pretty EPIC make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,STAY AWAY FROM THE\NBELL, YOU PEST!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,NONE of us can use\Nthe alicorn's magic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,until we figure\Nout how to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that fool's ridiculous\Nchaos magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord: I could\Nalways{\i1} tell{\i0} you how...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It would give you\Npower over all reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'd have\Nto ask nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,AND spare my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Discord! This\Nisn't the way to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[baby talk] Discord,\Ncould you pleeeease...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Threats are more\Nmy speed. SPEAK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lying! He\Nwon't tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly\Nwon't tell YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,after the way you lied to\NME last time we teamed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you musclebound cretin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This "cretin"\Ncould destroy you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,before you blink so choose\Nyour words carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. "Cretin"\Nis too polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How about 'pathetic\Ncentaur who uses magic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to compensate for the fact\Nthat deep down he's afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll never be enough
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to please dear old\NDad, King Vorak?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter] You missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight: Did he, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,GET HER!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [dramatic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. She's always\Nneeded you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Find Twilight! We may\Nnot have our magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but we aren't\N{\i1}completely{\i0} helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hold them off\Nas long as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That... was a\Npretty epic make up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just save Equestria! And\Nkeep Fluttershy safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you out\Nin the open? HIDE!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where IS everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The unicorns have\Nbeen gathering
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in Celestia's School of\NMagic ever since the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I was\Nheaded when I saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the earth\Nponies and pegasi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's everypony\Nfor themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That ain't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, YOU can all stand\Nout here and debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going where I'm safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis was\Ntelling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They really HAVE turned\Nponies against each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony's scared,\Nthat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to\Nget to Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and find\NTwilight pronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll know how to\Nset things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stay calm.\NI KNOW it seems bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's NO\Nneed to panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,GIVE US ONE GOOD\NREASON NOT TO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah..! Because Ponyville's\Nown heroes of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,are here to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd all these\Nponies come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth ponies been pourin' in\Nlooking for somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have unicorn\Nmagic to protect us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or a city in the sky to hide in\Nlike those cowardly pegasi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Cowardly!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [dramatic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're blocking\NCloudsdale!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Said they didn't want\Nany "grounded" ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,up in their business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! That's exactly what\NChrysalis and the others want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,More fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We know you're scared.\NWe're here to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,OH, YOU BETTER FIX THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's probably as\Nworried as everypony else
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and tryin' to find\Nsomewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was sure she'd be\Nwaitin' for us in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where else could she be!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I know where Twilight is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Thank Celestia\Nyou're all allright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's upstairs.\NIt's.. not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here!? I was so worried!\NWhere are the princesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They put up a CRAZY fight so\Nwe could escape and find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission Accomplished!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now LET'S SAVE\NEQUESTRIA! Woohoo, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They made a terrible\Nmistake. You all did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,From the second I got\Naway, I've been searching
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,every book, scroll and spell\Nfor a way to rescue you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop Chrysalis,\NTirek and Cozy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't found\Nanything! I've failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come up\Nwith something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't save\NEquestria without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You all escaped\Nwithout my help..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't need me then, so\Nwhy would anypony need me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We know things look bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but we've been in tough\Nspots before and we always-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Look around! Nothing we've\NEVER done has mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sombra? Returned and destroyed\Nthe Tree of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis? Tirek?\NCozy Glow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Returned and more\Npowerful than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The School of\NFriendship? Shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony in Equestria\Nis so blinded by fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't remember\Nwhat friendship IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,NOTHING we do makes\Nany difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But, WE'RE still\Nfree and together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not like things\Ncould get any worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't we learned NEVER\Nto say that by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,THE WINDIGOS!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfft! That's just a\NHearth's Warming Eve Story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Creatures made of wind that\Nspread cold and misery
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,across the land\Nto punish ponies!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems pretty real to me! Let\Nthe pegasi deal with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we\NCAN do except hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enchanted wind!\NWe can't control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can't rely on those\N{\i1}snooty{\i0} unicorns for any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Build up the cloudbank!\NWe'll try to block it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What about everypony\Ndown below?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're on their\Nown. We all are..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortify the shields around\Nthe school of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to protect ourselves.\NIt's all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do SOMETHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already\Ndone enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the truth,\NTwilight? Bad things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do,\Nthere's NEVER gonna be a time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when everything's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But that don't mean\Nyou quit trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT IF I MAKE\NTHINGS WORSE?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Celestia told\Nme I was taking over,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been gaining\Nconfidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I find out\Nit's all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria's been\Nfalling apart around us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't even notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of princess does\Nthat make ME? I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably know more about\Nbeing scared than anypony,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but thanks to all of you, I've\Nlearned I'm always LESS scared
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're facing\Nimpossible odds,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we're facing\Nthem together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what we always\Ndo, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're on our own and\Nwe have no idea what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true pretty much every\Ntime something terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the Elements\Nof Harmony anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you all be\Nso calm about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, even if YOU don't\Nbelieve you can do this, WE do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe in you. In us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, all our\Nlives wouldn't be the same
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,if we hadn't met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're better off because\Nof our friendship with YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when you say you\Nhaven't made a difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that's just not true! You've\Nmade a big difference.. to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Sometimes even\Nthe Princess of Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,needs a reminder that\Nthere's more to the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic of Friendship\Nthan rainbow lasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, that part\NIS pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We STILL need a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT sounds like the pony\NI used to foal-sit for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Count us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You need to stay here\Nand protect Flurry Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't... if\Nthings don't work out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,she's Equestria's\Nlast hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Three of our worst\Nvillains have taken over,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,powered up by\Nancient magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony in Equestria\Nis so scared and divided
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that the Windigos are circling\Nand it's up to us to fix it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna\Ndo, Twilight!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing we do\Nevery time, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Every prisoner is\Nsafely in their cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can hunt down the\Nrest of the- ..Windigos?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hunting anypony\Nd-d-down in THIS weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we magically get rid of\Nthem and w-w-warm things up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis: I don't\Nthink we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This could work out\Nquite well for me..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean US!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The harsh weather\Nis the final blow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to break the\Nponies' spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Equestria is\Na frozen wasteland,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll use our magic to\Ndestroy those windy beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies will be so grateful,\Nthey'll do whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Windigos are\Nancient magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be unwise to\Nleave them unchecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Best we deal\Nwith them NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We probably SHOULD deal with\NTwilight and her friends
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,before anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was too {\i1}cold{\i0} for\Nyou to hunt anypony down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need to!\NThey're RIGHT there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they\Nknow we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [dramatic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say they have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That bell has Discord, Celestia\Nand Luna's magic inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If they use it\Nagainst us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord's magic\Nis so chaotic,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,he's the only one\Nwho can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't accept\Nthat you were beaten
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,before you even realized\Nthere was a fight, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat us\Nif we never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have my\Nfriends by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put my faith\Nin Friend--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Can we get on\Nwith this please!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get that bell and\Nget Discord and the princesses
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,their magic back! Rainbow\NDash, Pinkie, you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet! I'll grab\Nthat bell in ten seconds-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We're the distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're{\i0} going to\Nget the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, come out\Nwherever you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,THERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Step right up evil fillies\Nand gentlevillains!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Try your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Missed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Close, but no\Ncherry chimichanga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggle] Thanks for playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they have to\Nbe so ANNOYING?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not annoying...\Ndistracting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now Professor. We all\Nknow {\i1}you're{\i0} not the {\i1}fast{\i0} one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,ENOUGH! Or the dragon's\Nwings get plucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE! Don't hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me!\NJust save-Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out that the\N"magic" of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is your biggest\Nweakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A fitting end to\Nyour PATHETIC story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, we\Nface it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: What happened?\NCan I open my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack: You sure can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [trumpet fanfare] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Which ones!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The changelings won't\Nfool them forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know how long the\Nunicorn's shield will hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you all {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gallus: That's kinda {\i1}our{\i0} fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know those long\Nlectures about friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you gave at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know the story of\NHearth's Warming Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We can defeat the\NWindigos TOGETHER!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You REALLY think if we\Nall sing a couple songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,everything will be fine!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not JUST\Nsinging that saved
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the founders of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what it {\i1}represented{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...earth ponies, unicorns and\Npegasi becoming FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We learned at Twilight's\NSchool that friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is the most powerful\Nmagic there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Focusing on our differences\Nkeeps us divided!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Villains and creatures\Nlike the Windigos
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,use that division\Nagainst us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks strong.\NPonies strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But yaks and ponies\Nstronger TOGETHER!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks must be LOYAL\Nto pony friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know helping\Nother creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,by being KIND and\NGENEROUS sounds lame..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've SEEN how\Npowerful it can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing together,\Nsinging together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,even LAUGHING\Ntogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT'S what real\Nheroes look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Were we really\Nhappy by ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,at the bottom of the\Nocean? Be honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ponies that\Nshowed us a better way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They've taught us\Nhow powerful love
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and the MAGIC of\Nfriendship truly is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them\Nstand alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're their friends.\NThey need us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack: How\N'bout that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like you said the\Nday we opened that school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The more creatures who\Nknow about friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the safer we'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We TOLD you you had\Nit all figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ [dramatic music] ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [music intensifies] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: ENOUGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you,\NI almost lost my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But every creature\Nhere has reminded me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of the true power\Nof friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There will always be\Ndarkness in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But there will also always\Nbe those who find the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pillars knew this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they created\Nthe Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elements showed\Nme and my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,how strong our\Nfriendship could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Together we worked to bring\Nharmony to Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But there will\NALWAYS be more to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why we teach others\Nabout the magic of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Others who will continue our\Nmission after we are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I truly understand. The\Nelements were just symbols.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The real magic has\Nalways been right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And the more who understand\Nhow powerful friendship is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the stronger we\Nwill all be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [majestic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You think FRIENDSHIP\Nwill save you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We will ALWAYS return!\NNOTHING will EVER stop-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate rain..?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie! You took Discord's magic\Nfrom the bell!? How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm! Tingly. Itchy. Also like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I COULD TRANSFORM\NTHE COSMOS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,SO EVERYTHING IS\NMADE OF ICING!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps maybe I should...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiter!? There's some\Nchaos in my soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a punishment\NWORTHY of all you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That DOES\Nseem fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help?\NPlease..?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything\Nthat they would want LESS!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: When I sent you to\NPonyville, I had high hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When you became\NPrincess of Friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I made the\Nright choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing could prepare me\Nfor how proud I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria is definitely\Nin the right hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You.. are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?\NI think I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! First\Nquestion, Your Highness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,what do we do with\Nall these creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna need a LOT more\Nchairs for the coronation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, as ruler\Nof Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to postpone the\Ncoronation for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At least until the\Ncastle's rebuilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's something\NWE need to do first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Post apocalyptic\Ndonuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. But there's gonna\Nbe plenty of time for all
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the challenges and struggles\Nand adventures to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I just want to\Nspend a quiet moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with the six best\Nfriends I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, mostly quiet..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the\Nend of an era.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,OR the beginning of an\Neven more AWESOME era!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know is whatever comes\Nnext is going to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,With you guys by my\Nside, how could it not?
